title: Quarter-Season Awards: MVP, Rookie of the Year, and More
description:
Nora and Mal give out some awards after the first month of the season. They hand out MVP, Rookie of the Year, a listener-chosen award, and much more (2:45).

Hosts: Nora Princiotti and Mallory Rubin
Production Assistant: Isaiah Blakely
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
